#### **3. New Export Format**

```javascript
// Add to export system
function exportToCSV() {
    const csvContent = this.favorites.map(fav => 
        `"${fav.text}","${fav.topic}","${fav.language}","${fav.timestamp}"`
    ).join('\n');
    
    const header = 'Prompt,Topic,Language,Date\n';
    this.downloadFile(header + csvContent, 'favorites.csv', 'text/csv');
}
```

